getText

public java.lang.String getText()
This returns the text in the contenteditable div. There seems to be an issue with innerText. String operation application were failing on the innerText like trim() etc. Hence, to get the text. First have taken the innerHTML and then replaced all the space characters with " ". Then putting this HTML in a HTML Element and taken its text value.
